### HRM API Test Requests

# Test environment variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5152
@contentType = application/json

### Get all departments
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/departments
Accept: {{contentType}}

### Get active departments only
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/departments/active
Accept: {{contentType}}

### Get department by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/departments/1
Accept: {{contentType}}

### Create a new department
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/departments
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Marketing",
  "description": "Marketing and Sales Department",
  "isActive": true
}

### Update a department (use ID from created department)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/departments/4
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Marketing & Sales",
  "description": "Marketing, Sales and Customer Relations Department",
  "isActive": true
}

### Delete a department (use ID from created department)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/departments/4

### Get all employees
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/employees
Accept: {{contentType}}

### Get employee by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/employees/1
Accept: {{contentType}}

